00:59:40.307 --> 00:59:41.850
About that reporter…

00:59:41.934 --> 00:59:43.769
There's something different
about her articles now.

00:59:44.353 --> 00:59:46.605
She used to be a political reporter?

00:59:46.688 --> 00:59:49.108
-Wait, who?
